Package org.acumos.federation.gateway

Interface PeerService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PeerServiceImpl
    public interface PeerService
    API for accessing information about peers and related items. Provides a mechanism for looking up all or specific peers, for requesting and cancelling peer registration, and for accessing subscriptions to peers.
